<h1 >Donate Supplies to Ms. Fisher's Classroom</h1>
<h2> Supplies List</h2>
<p>Thank you for taking time to visit this web page and donating a needed classroom supply item.<br>
The donated supplies will help the teaching and learning of computer science be more interactive and meaningful!</p>
<table>
    <tr id='table_header'><td>Supply</td><td>Total Quantity Needed</td><td>Quantity Still Needed</td></tr>
    {{#each supplies}}
        <tr><td>{{this.supply_name}}</td><td>{{this.total_quantity_needed}} </td><td>{{this.quantity_still_needed}}</td></tr>
    {{/each}}   
</table>

<form action = '/addDonationForm' method = 'post'>
 <h2>Donate a Supply Item</h2>
 <ul><li>Enter your first name, last name, email address and class period.</li>
 <li>Select a supply item from the dropdown menu that is still needed. </li>
 <li>Then press submit. </li>
</ul>
<p>A confirmation message will be emailed to you. </p>

    <label for id='fname' >First name:  </label><input type = 'text' name = 'fname' required> <br>
    <label for id='lname' >Last name:  </label><input type = 'text' name = 'lname' required> <br>
    <label for id='email' >Email:  </label><input type='email' name = 'email' required> <br>
    <label for id='period' >Class Period:  </label><select name='period' required><br>    
    <option value="" disabled selected> Select a class period</option>
    <option value=1>1st</option>
    <option value=2>2nd</option>
    <option value=4>4th</option>
    <option value=5>5th</option>
    <option value=6>6th</option>
    <option value=-1>N/A</option>
    </select><br>
    <label for id='supply'>Supplies:  </label><select  name = 'supply_id' required>
        <option value ="" disabled selected> Select a supply item below</option>
        {{#each supplies}}
            {{#if this.quantity_still_needed}}
                <option value = {{this.supply_id}}>{{this.supply_name}}</option>
            {{/if}}
        {{/each}}
    </select>
    <input id='submit_button' type="submit"></input>
 
</form>

